Package edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamondModel.Card.CharacterCards

This is the package for all the character specific cards in the game.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CripplingTrap
    This is the Hunter class card Crippling Trap, but this is an extension feature that we are not implementing right now.
    Duplicate
    This is the Mage character card which allows the player to: Copy a card from your hand into your hand.
    Meditate
    This is the Philosopher character card which allows the player to: Draw 2 cards.
    Nightmare
    This is the Demon character card which allows the player to: Discard a random card from an opponent's hand.
    Prayer
    This is the Priest character card which allows the player to: Restore 12/14/16/18/20 health, depending on the character's level.
    SeismicSlam
    This is the Berserker character card which allows the player to: Deal 12/14/16/18/20 damage to a monster, depending on the character's level.
    ShieldToss
    This is the Royal Guard character card which allows the player to: Stun an opponent for 1 turn.
    Sprint
    This is the Scout character card which allows the player to: Move 2/2/3/4/5 tiles, depending on the character's level.
